Thibaud Jean Vallet, 24, and his cousin Jean Mickael Batrikian, 18, used a deodorant can and lighter to set the marsupial alight in Rottnest Island on April 3 .
The men pleaded guilty to animal cruelty at Fremantle Magistrate's Court on Friday .
They were each fined $4000 and will be held behind bars for seven days if they fail to pay the fines .